parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the alternator/stator can cause the electrical system to shut down, leading to a loss of power and potentially causing accidents or leaving the rider stranded.
The electrical system shutdown can cause the engine to stall, leading to a loss of control and potentially causing accidents or leaving the rider stranded.
The mismatched stator/rotor combination can cause the stator to fail, leading to a loss of power and potentially causing accidents or leaving the rider stranded.
The failure of the camshaft bearing can cause the engine to stop running, leading to a loss of power and control, which can result in accidents or leave the rider stranded on a busy highway.
The failure of the cam chain tensioner can cause the engine to stop running, leading to a loss of power and control, which can result in accidents or leave the rider stranded.
symptoms: Large chunk of material blocking oil flow

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The fracture of the swing arm and failure of the belt drive can cause the motorcycle to wobble and shake, leading to a loss of control and potentially resulting in accidents or injuries.
